body:
This Mod is an addon for Cobblemon, where it adds other versions of mimikyu (same move set and type, the only change is in the model and spawn location);
> **Pipikyu** (Mimikyu + Pumpkaboo) they spawn in Spooky Biomes on the Uncommon bucket levels between 20-38;

> **Eiskyu** (Mimikyu + Eiscue) they spawn in Frozen Ocean on the Uncommon bucket levels between 20-38;

> **GmaxMimikyu** they spawn in Spooky Biomes on the Uncommon bucket levels between 20-38;

> **Unite** they spawn in Spooky Biomes on the rare bucket levels between 39-52;
